1. *Njihovom* kućom upravlja majka. (Their house is managed by their mother.)
2. Zadovoljni su *njihovom* odlukom. (They are satisfied with their decision.)
3. Pitali su me o *njihovom* iskustvu. (They asked me about their experience.)
4. *Njihovom* radu treba dati priznanje. (Their work deserves recognition.)
5. *Njihovom* izboru nema alternative. (There is no alternative to their choice.)
6. Rekao sam *njihovoj* prijateljici da će se kasniti. (I told their friend that they would be late.)
7. Uživaju u *njihovom* društvu. (They enjoy their company.)
8. Molim vas da mi date informacije o *njihovom* dolasku. (Please give me information about their arrival.)
9. Uvek se iznenadim *njihovom* kreativnošću. (I am always amazed by their creativity.)
10. Planirate li da se vidite sa *njihovom* porodicom? (Are you planning to meet with their family?)

Note: In Serbian, the word "njihovom" is a form of the possessive pronoun "njihov" which means "their" in English.